; jit-profile-receipt-band.fk - witness the first Form-native JIT optimizer
; receipt/category rung.
;
; Verdict 127 when every claim lands:
;   1   two per-instance array receipts collapse to the same category signature
;   2   a changed shape changes the category signature
;   4   hot pure mono array receipt yields crystallize+inline+stack+field+index+CPU
;   8   hot pure mono hashmap receipt yields crystallize+inline+hash+CPU
;   16  ordered red-black tree receipt yields crystallize+tree
;   32  a cool guard-deopt receipt asks to melt
;   64  GPU buffer/range receipt yields crystallize+index+GPU
;
; Run:
;   ( cat observe/jit-profile-receipt.fk observe/tests/jit-profile-receipt-band.fk ) > /tmp/jpr.fk
;   ./fkwu --src /tmp/jpr.fk

(do (jit-profile-receipt-check))
